Latvia’s Ventspils to Double Coal Traffic in 2011, PortNews Says

-- B y   A l i s t a i r   H o l l o w a y
-- 
2011-05-27T07:06:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-27/latvia-s-ventspils-to-double-coal-traffic-in-2011-portnews-says.html
The Baltic Coal Terminal, based in
 Latvia ’s Ventspils port, expects to double its coal handling
this year to 4 million metric tons compared with 2010,
 PortNews  reported, citing Board Chairman Ilya Sokolov.  To contact the reporter on this story:
